378
00:32:06,700 --> 00:32:09,430
- Ešte nie...<br>- Nechajme to tak.

379
00:32:09,430 --> 00:32:11,840
Neskôr si vypočujem vaše odpoveď.

380
00:32:22,000 --> 00:32:24,260
